        <h2>About AHP</h2>
        <p>At AHP, everything begins with three things I care deeply about: <strong>design, data, and fun</strong>. I picked up a guitar in my teens, fell head over cleats for cycling later on, and haven't stopped tinkering since. ACP launched in 2023 to bring a bit of cheeky charm to cyclists' gift boxes. AGP followed in 2024, giving guitarists their own slice of the fun.</p>
        
        <p>Every product starts with a simple interrogation (of myself):</p>
        <ul class="interrogation-list">
          <li>Does it make sense to someone who's not inside my head?</li>
          <li>Is it beautifully built—design-wise and materials-wise? This is giftware, not landfill.</li>
          <li>And most of all, how will it land with the person unwrapping it? Will it spark joy and hold their attention once the novelty's worn off?</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>That's the aim. To make things people actually want to keep. Not just because they look good but because they feel right. Gifts with a bit of soul, a lot of thought, and no tat.</p>
        
